# AI System Rules

This project uses a unified AI system for session management.

## Entry Points

- Universal: `AGENTS.md`
- Definitions: `.ai/`
- Local state: `.ai-local/` (gitignored)

## Commands

### boot
Start session, load context from memory layers.
Run: `.ai/session/scripts/boot.sh`
Then read: `.ai-local/CONTEXT.md`

### save
Save session state, propose commit.
Run: `.ai/session/scripts/save.sh`
Then update: `.ai-local/STATE.md` and `.ai-local/HISTORY.md`

## Memory Layers

- L0: Current chat
- L1: `.ai-local/STATE.md` (~3 sessions)
- L2: `.ai-local/HISTORY.md` (all sessions)
- L3: Git commits (forever)

## Documentation

- `.ai/README.md` - System overview
- `.ai/session/README.md` - Memory concepts
- `.ai/skills/` - Skill definitions
